entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Amazingly, you have retrieved the diagnostic controller from the squill cave. That's quite an accomplishment.
entries.journal_entry_description: Watto seems to think the diagnostic controller is deep inside the notorious squill cave. It's going to take a fast gun and a stout heart to pull this one off.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Watto has given you directions to the squill cave. This is where he thinks the diagnostic controller can be found.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Recover the Droid Diagnostic Controller from the Squill Cave
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Apparently the man that bought the part from Watto found who he was looking for. The old man didn't seem to mind me taking the diagnostic controller. Maybe he wanted me to come down there. Who knows.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Good Work! You have completed the Squill Diving quest.
